Hello Bioconductor community,

Since releasing the 3.11.0 versions of the db0 packages, we have added in more recent GO information. Therefore a newer 3.11.1 version of db0s are now available (arabidopsis.db0 is now at version 3.11.2).

The new OrgDbs and TxDbs for Bioconductor 3.11 are now available.

